DLC Content:

ULTRA STREET FIGHTER IV - UPGRADE PACK
- New challengers Decapre, Elena, Hugo, Poison, and Rolento join the fight for a total of 44 characters.
- Features many extra stuff like balance updates, new stages and YouTube upload.
- Six new stages, all of which are from Street Fighter X Tekken.
- Alternate costumes are excluded, so dont forget to download Ultra Complete Alternate Costume Pack (all 7 Ultra Packs included).
- IMPORTANT: Once you update your game to ULTRA, you will not be able to downgrade to Super SFIV and Super SFIV Arcade Edition unless you delete your game and reinstall.

ULTRA STREET FIGHTER IV - 2014 CHALLENGERS PACK
- Access to the 2014 Challengers Pack, which consists of five unique character costumes.
- Jungle Elena, Medieval Hugo, Pirate Poison, Wizard Rolento, Gladiator Decapre.

ULTRA STREET FIGHTER IV - 2014 COSTUME COMPATIBILITY PACK
- Required to install for costumes to appear in game.

ULTRA COMPLETE ALTERNATE COSTUME PACK
- Bundled ultra-powered pack of alternate costumes for SSFIV and SSFIV: AE.
- All seven packs in one: Ultra Challengers Pack 1 & 2, Ultra Brawler Pack, Ultra Classic Pack, Ultra Femme Fatales Pack, Ultra Shadaloo Pack, Ultra Shoryuken Pack.
- Every character's Ultra Alternate Costume is included in this pack.
- New Ultra costumes for Hakan, Makoto, Guy, Dudley and Dee Jay.
- New Ultra costumes for Juri, Ibuki, Cody, Adon and T.Hawk.
- New Ultra costumes for Zangief, E.Honda, Rufus, Abel and El Fuerte.
- New Ultra costumes for Guile, Blanka, Dhalsim, Gen and Fei Long.
- New Ultra costumes for Chun-Li, C.Viper, Sakura, Rose and Cammy.
- New Ultra costumes for Balrog, Sagat, Vega, M.Bison and Seth.
- New Ultra costumes for Ryu, Ken, Gouken, Dan and Akuma.

SUPER COMPLETE ALTERNATE COSTUME PACK
- Bundled Super-powered pack of alternate costumes for SSFIV and SSFIV: AE.
- Outfit every character in the game with brand new threads.
- All seven packs in one: Super Challengers Costume Pack 1 & 2, Super Brawler Pack, Super Classic Pack, Super Femme Fatales Pack, Super Shadaloo Pack, Super Shoryuken Pack.
- New Super costumes for Hakan, Makoto, Guy, Dudley and Dee Jay.
- New Super costumes for Juri, Ibuki, Cody, Adon and T.Hawk.
- New Super costumes for Zangief, E.Honda, Rufus, Abel and El Fuerte.
- New Super costumes for Guile, Blanka, Dhalsim, Gen and Fei Long.
- New Super costumes for Chun-Li, C.Viper, Sakura, Rose and Cammy.
- New Super costumes for Balrog, Sagat, Vega, M.Bison and Seth.
- New Super costumes for Ryu, Ken, Gouken, Dan and Akuma.

ARCADE CHALLENGERS PACK
- Alternate costumes for Yun, Yang, Evil Ryu and Oni.
- There are a total of eight costumes in this pack.
- This pack require Arcade Edition or its upgrade to use it.
